  "title": "Office Cleaner",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Perform general office cleaning tasks, including dusting, mopping, and vacuuming</li>\n  <li>Clean and sanitize the pantry, restrooms, and shared spaces</li>\n  <li>Empty trash bins and handle proper waste disposal</li>\n  <li>Restock essential supplies such as toilet paper, soap, and paper towels</li>\n  <li>Ensure the office remains clean, hygienic, and well-organized</li>\n  <li>Prepare beverages for staff and guests as needed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
